person in other respects as well.

00:04:41.740 --> 00:04:45.580
Not only is she a dominant
figure in television now,

00:04:45.580 --> 00:04:48.470
but she's an incredible
mother to her 3 children,

00:04:48.470 --> 00:04:49.950
she's also a great philanthropist.

00:04:49.950 --> 00:04:52.570
She just came from the African
American History and Culture Museum

00:04:52.570 --> 00:04:54.510
