million dollars.

00:04:54.510 --> 00:05:03.700
[ Applause ]

00:05:03.700 --> 00:05:05.950
And I have the pleasure
of having her serve

00:05:05.950 --> 00:05:07.250
on the Kennedy Center Board

00:05:07.250 --> 00:05:09.410
of Trustees appointed
by President Obama.

00:05:09.410 --> 00:05:12.510
So it's my pleasure to
welcome Shonda Rhimes.

00:05:12.510 --> 00:05:20.690
[ Applause, Cheering ]

00:05:20.690 --> 00:05:22.610
Okay, thank you.

